title: Do These Things To Lose Weight During Covid-19
itunes:title: Do These Things To Lose Weight During Covid-19
description:
I've been paying a lot of attention to what my listeners need right now. And what I'm seeing is a lot of you need help figuring out what to do with extra time, prioritizing your to do lists, and keeping yourself sane while we wait out coronavirus.
 
Today's podcast is full of amazing tips and ideas to make sure you are staying productive both physically and emotionally. I tell you how to get things done and how to stay out of the pantry. I also give you ideas on how to collect resources that are exactly what you need right now.
 
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
